ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
Customer Relationship Management (CRM) systems often contain inaccurate or duplicate data, leading to inefficiencies in business operations. This project leverages AI-driven techniques to improve data accuracy in CRM by detecting anomalies, filtering incorrect entries, and enhancing overall data reliability.

ğŸš€ Features
AI-Powered Anomaly Detection: Identifies incorrect, duplicate, or suspicious data.
Data Accuracy Visualization: Graphical insights into CRM data accuracy improvements.
Confusion Matrix Evaluation: Assessing the model's performance in detecting errors.
User-Friendly Dashboard: Upload and analyze CRM datasets with interactive charts.
Automated Data Cleaning: Improves CRM data accuracy through AI-based filtering.
